spans.text: The forms that fleet through life's deceitful dream
Glittering in beams of visionary day
That soul-expressing eye , benignly bright , Where Meekness beams ineffable delight ; That brow , where Wisdom
let me listen , while her words impart The sweet effusions of the blameless heart
me listen , while her words impart The sweet effusions of the blameless heart
the faded cheek with rosy glow
all its beauties withering in the dust
Infusing balm into the rankled soul ! — OH Death , why arm with cruelty thy power , And spare the weed , yet lop the lovely flower
Virtue for the lingering morn , On this dark wild condemned to roam forlorn
that bursts the bonds of clay
The hopeless Parent , Husband , Brother , Friend
thy strain , Nor Sorrow's dread solemnity profane
her dust , in speechless anguish , bend The hopeless Parent , Husband , Brother , Friend ! — How vain the hope of Man ! — But cease thy strain , Nor Sorrow's dread solemnity profane
